Package: pubtal
Version: 3.5-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Luis Rodrigo Gallardo Cruz <rodrigo@debian.org>
Installed-Size: 668
Depends: python (>= 2.6.6-7~), python-simpletal (>= 4.1-6)
Suggests: python-textile (>= 1:2.1.4)
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://www.owlfish.com/software/PubTal/index.html
Description: Template driven web site builder for small sites
 PubTal uses the ZPT language from ZOPE and input plugins to
 generate a web site, maintaining content separate from presentation.
 .
 Input can be provided in several formats, including plain text, abiword,
 and textile, if the python-textile package is installed.
